n8n_test_mode_note: In test mode, you must click 'Execute Workflow' button in N8N editor before each webhook call
production_setup: For continuous operation, activate the workflow (toggle switch) to use production webhook URLs
instructions:
Your application sends real-time date data. To see it in N8N:
1. Open your workflow in N8N editor
2. Click 'Execute Workflow' button
3. Immediately interact with the website (click calendar dates)
4. Check N8N executions list for received data
